name: PhiBrows 12-Pins 4Bunch 3-Round Blades 50pcs
short_description: Shading 12 pins blade with 4 Rows  of 3 Round needles, with extremely high elasticity and flexibility. The unique created spaces in between needles imitate extremely good looking natural dots effect of the shading. suitable only for PHIGLOW HOLDER
long_description: This blade provides much faster operation of coloring resulting with very subtle shading effect at the same time. Easy to operate, high efficiency, less skin trauma.  Premium quality stainless steel needle tips that deposit pigment quickly and evenly. Each needle has been pre-sterilized and individually blister packed with the latest sealing technology ,completely protected from physical damages, ensuring that your product will arrive in perfect condition.
